'''Top OpEx''' was the position given to higher ranking members of the [[SoroSuub Corporation/Legends|SoroSuub Corporation]] when they were given control of an entire [[Star system/Legends|system]]. [[Tyanna Tymb]] was given this title when she was given control of the [[Varada system/Legends|Varada system]].

